member.name: T:Gtk.Application
member.remarks: Provides the initialization and event loop iteration related methods for the GTK widget library. Since GTK is an event driven toolkit, Applications register callbacks against various events to handle user input. These callbacks are invoked from the main event loop when events are detected.
